    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/06/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8090984757967432360.png",
                "id": "talent29079",
                "key": "Den of Thunder",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Den of Thunder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p>If the target is already affected by Electro, steal 1 Energy from them. (If this character's Energy is already full, then the stolen Energy will be given to the next character who does not have full Energy)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/18/35428890/103d1f8ccc183cfd373cdbd58e61a480_2781454740667805971.png",
                "id": "talent31857",
                "key": "Shock of the Enigmatic Abyss",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Shock of the Enigmatic Abyss"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p>If the target has no more than 1 Energy, deals +2 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/18/35428890/61b0d12e2b924a2ae4ddb9665a2bb138_2109792420733986679.png",
                "id": "talent24486",
                "key": "Wild Thunderburst",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Wild Thunderburst"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains Electric Rebirth.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Electric Rebirth</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached would be defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure the character gains<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Immunity to Defeat</span>, and heals them to 4 HP. After this effect is triggered, this character deals +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong></p><p>Certain effects will grant characters an<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.</p><p>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat</span>. (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/06/35428890/594963a560726b1248fca6760ce6a894_1291922755107350613.png",
                "id": "talent73807",
                "key": "Electric Rebirth",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Electric Rebirth"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/06/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_6359071531943740185.png",
                "id": "talent71660",
                "key": "Electric DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Electric DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Energy</span></strong><br>Characters must consume Energy to use their Elemental Bursts.<br>When characters use an Elemental Skill or a Normal Attack, they will gain 1 Energy.</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/06/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8922799166442384038.png",
