                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow...\" \"Beneath the abyssal depths, legends say that in the pitch-blackness lives a huge purple monster, and the amount of Electro on its body can cause cats to flee in fear even from hundreds of paces away...\"",
