                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: \"Abyss Lector: Violet Lightning\" starts with the Talent Card \"Chain Lightning Cascade\" equipped; after triggering \"Electric Rebirth\", it attaches \"Thunderous Ward\" to itself. \"Abyss Herald: Wicked Torrents\" starts with the Talent Card \"Surging Undercurrent\" equipped. After triggering \"Watery Rebirth,\" they will gain a \"Surging Ward.\"",
